PLAYER STATS HELP
WILLPOWER
Willpower(WIL): Willpower is a measurement of your character's desire to live and the strength of their personality. It plays a very important role during combat and will eventually be used in some types of magic. It will be one of the primary factors in resisting harmful spells.

See also: ~CREFstats, strength, dexterity, constitution, speed, intelligence, empathy, charisma
